_sText:
Map from Half Life 2 Episode 2 Ported to CS with hostage rescue mod!

WARNING!! Map Have Custom particles!!
Install if particles for work: last steam version v88 or 89 instal all in "Steam\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\custom\cs_outland\

CT's Have 2 Spawn points, T's need to rushing on locations, were hostages camping.
one Three near location from CT works as ladder! 
Map have a 3 Hostage rescue point and 3 Hostages.
Ideal map For Snipers!

Plot
The pilot rescuing people, was seriously wounded, not reaching the place of evacuation made a forced landing.
People ran to the nearest place of outland, in search of medicines.
SWAT went to help people, but the cars were mired in the mud.
The terrorists were not distracted when they learned of the problems of the special forces on the radio were pushed to the place, but alas there was not enough 
gasoline. Got Smoke grenades and storm the place,
Do not let terrorists take hostages!
